Using advanced technology align27 decode your birth chart using thousands of time-tested ancient astrology techniques to give you hyper - personalised, real-time personalised data every minute of the day.
Empowering you to manage, maximize and master your own time.

align27 will tip you off about the best time to do things and vice versa, so you can maximise your 1,440 minutes a day and get things done quicker with the results you want. It’s like having a secret superpower in your pocket.
align27 got you pro enthusiasts covered with Advanced Rituals and Hora, Panchapakshi, Panchak and Ascendant shown on a real-time grid.
Dive into this magnificent world of aligning your work patterns, scheduling your meetings, reserving tricky conversations to optimum times and asking the bank for money, just by referring to align27 for less than 2 mins a day.
